    <h1 class="section-title">Visionary Development Grounded in Portuguese Heritage</h1>
    <p>Amora Vida is a visionary development group with Portuguese roots and international investor backing, focused on transforming strategic land into resilient communities. We activate heritage-rich sites and growth corridors across Greater Lisbon, partnering with municipalities to deliver projects that respect local character and global standards.</p>
